PrecisEnactment of the MILITARY VALOUR DECORATIONS REGULATIONS - which provide for the creation and awarding in Canada of Military Valour Decorations that are to be designated and styled as the Victoria Cross, the Star of Military Valour and the Medal of Military Valour.
